

How can the system scale up live price updates?
  -> Polling exchange -> Very bad because we will keep polling exchange for same information and it might not have been updated
  -> Polling Internal Cache -> Internal cache acts as a proxy -> only drawback is we still poll when price is not updated.
  -> SSE -> Best approach, only send updates. Challenge is how disconnect and reconnets works


